<body>
  <%- include('../partials/nav_partial', { currentPage: null }) %>

  <div id="main-content-container">
    <h1>WELCOME TO VIBE CHECK!</h1>
    <div id="instructions-container">
      The ultimate game to test if you can manage people.<br><br>
      Each character has a different difficulty level (1, 2, or 3).<br><br>
      When you interact with a character:<br>
      - Positive actions increase their health by 5.<br>
      - Negative actions decrease their health by 10.<br><br>
      Your score changes based on 5 × the character's difficulty.<br><br>
      Some actions cost money. You start with $50!<br>
      If you can't afford any actions, you can ignore a character (but it will hurt your score).<br><br>
      Ignoring characters over multiple rounds also decreases their health.<br><br>
      Make a character happy enough, and they may start paying you!<br><br>
      But beware — if a character loses all their health, the game is over!
    </div>
  </div>

